    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNo formal interface for viewing/editing logfiles.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nOpen to better ideas, but here's a drive-by thought:\n\n- `:editlog foo` opens the \"foo\" log found in `stdpath('log')`.\n- `:editlog <tab>` completes discovered logfiles.\n- `:editlog` opens the `stdpath('log')` directory.\n\nUh... we should probably add a `logs/` dir... `stdpath('log')` currently just opens `stdpath('state')`.",
