        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Or if following the `:lsp` approach with sub-commands:\n\n`:log level <component> <level>`\n`:log edit <file|component>` - even if the primary action is viewing, it matches `:e`, and imho it doesn't have to mark the buffer as unmodifiable. Being able to do stuff like `:g//d` to filter out irrelevant entries can actually be useful.",
            "created_at": "2026-03-31T14:00:34Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/35082#issuecomment-4162878728",
