        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "> Or if following the `:lsp` approach with sub-commands:\n\nWhile it was a good idea for `:lsp`, I don't believe it should be done for `:log`.\n\n> imho it doesn't have to mark the buffer as unmodifiable\n\nEarlier I had made `:log` set `'readonly'`, but I have since dropped that line. So agreed.",
